|-
| 2005 || {{dts|May}} || Detention center || Start || || The {{w|South Texas Detention Facility}}, a privately operated prison, opens for operation in {{w|Pearsall, Texas}} as the Pearsall Immigration Detention Center. The prison houses people for the {{w|U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement}} as well as {{w|United States Marshal Service}}. || Texas || South Texas Detention Facility, Pearsall
