| 2007 || {{dts|July 6}} || Detention standards || Criticism/challenge || ICE, Government Accountability Office (GAO) || A report by the Government Accountability Office (GAO) covering 23 detention centers shows significant telephone access problems but no pattern of noncompliance for other standards GAO reviewed.<ref>{{cite web|url = https://www.gao.gov/products/gao-07-875|title = Alien Detention Standards: Telephone Access Problems Were Pervasive at Detention Facilities; Other Deficiencies Did Not Show a Pattern of Noncompliance|date = July 6, 2007|accessdate = July 4, 2021|publisher = U.S. Government Accountability Office}}</ref>
