| 2007 || || Detention standards (monitoring) || Start || ICE, Nakamoto Group || ICE enters into a contract with the Nakamoto Group that is a "monthly monitoring contract" that "involved monthly technical assistance visits to mostly ICE detention facilities and included full-time technicall assistance compliance reviewers at the forty largest ICE detention facilities."<ref name=nakamoto-response/>
