| 2010 || || Detention standards (monitoring) || Update || ICE, Nakamoto Group || ICE insources its monthly monitoring program of its largest detention centers, that had previously been handled by the Nakamoto Group on contract. Nakamoto Group would continue to be used by ICE for required annual inspections of detention centers based on ICE checklists.<ref name=nakamoto-response/>
